[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"de","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor 6 Monaten","text":"Wir hatten das Brühe-Fondue und LIEBTEN den Salat und das Gemüse. Fleisch ist Fleisch, das in Brühe gekocht wird, also war es nicht allzu spannend. Ich würde etwas anderes ausprobieren, das weniger touristisch ist. Das „Französische“ Dressing war fantastisch! Es erinnerte uns Amerikaner an ein vereinfachtes Ranch-Dressing, aber definitiv kein Ranch-Dressing!

Die Einrichtung ist neuer als alles andere, was wir auf dieser Reise ausprobiert haben. Erinnert an ein „Kongress“-Zentrum ähnliches Hotel in den Staaten. Das Personal war reizend und die Nussmischung an der Bar ist ein Muss!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"de","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor 2 Monaten","text":"Das Essen ist einfach großartig. Hatten Rindfleischbrühe mit Pfannkuchen, Rindfleisch auf heißen Steinen, das man selbst zubereiten muss, Brokkoli. Die Atmosphäre ist schön, die Aussicht großartig, die Kellner professionell.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"de","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"War zweimal dort, das erste Mal lief alles gut, das Essen war köstlich, das Eierschwammerl-Gulasch ist ein Muss :)
Allerdings gab es beim zweiten Mal ein paar Enttäuschungen - das Nudelgericht wurde fast kalt serviert, die Ramen-Suppe war extrem salzig, konnte sie kaum essen und kann geschmacklich nicht wirklich mit einem echten Ramen verglichen werden. Zum Nachtisch gab es nur einen Becher verpacktes Eis, das leider schon alt und nicht gut war, also gaben wir es zurück. Der Service ist extrem nett und freundlich, angenehme Atmosphäre. Insgesamt könnten ein paar Kleinigkeiten verbessert werden, aber wir werden sicherlich für einen weiteren Versuch wiederkommen.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"de","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"Das Restaurant hat eine sehr gemütliche Inneneinrichtung und wir hatten das Glück, an einem ruhigen Mittwochabend zu essen.

Wir bestellten Edamame, Caesar Salat, Schnitzel und Ramen-Suppe.
Alles war sehr lecker, nur die Portion der Ramen-Suppe war nicht genug für ein Hauptgericht. Und die Kartoffeln zum Schnitzel waren etwas geschmacklos.

Unser Kellner war sehr aufmerksam und freundlich.

Ein guter Abend und ein großartiger Ort für ein Abendessen mit leckerem Essen!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"de","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"vor einem Jahr","text":"Sehr angenehmes Mittagessen an einem großartigen Ort.
Das Essen war wirklich gut und seinen Preis wert, die Atmosphäre war sehr eindrucksvoll, besonders dank der großartigen Aussicht aus den großen Fenstern auf die Landschaft.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"6 months ago","text":"We had the broth fondue and LOVED the salad and veggies.  Meat is meat cooked in broth so it was not too exciting. I would try something else and less touristy. The “French” dressing was fantastic! It reminded us Americans of a simplified ranch dressing, but definitely not ranch dressing!

The facility is newer than everything else we have tried on this trip. Reminiscent of a “convention” center type hotel in the states.  Staff was lovely and the nut mix at the bar is a must try!","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"2 months ago","text":"The food is just great. Had beef broth with pancakes, beef on hot stones you have to bake yourself, brokoli. The atmosphere is nice, the views great, waiters professional.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"Went there 2 times, first time everything went well, food was delicious, eierschwammerl goulash is a must try :)
However second time there were a few let downs - pasta dish was served almost cold, ramen soup was extremely salty, couldn’t hardly eat it and can’t really compare to an actual ramen in depth of flavor. For dessert there was a choice of packaged cup of ice cream which, unfortunately, was old and not good so we returned it back. Service is extremely nice and friendly, pleasant atmosphere. Overall, a little bits and pieces could be improved but we’ll certainly come back again for another try.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"The restaurant has a very cozy interior design and we were lucky to eat on a quiet Wednesday evening.

We ordered Edamame, Caesar salad, Schnitzel and Ramen soup.
Everything was very delicious, just the portion of the Ramen soup was not enough for a main course. And the potatoes to the Schnitzel were a little tasteless.

Our waiter was very attentive and friendly.

A good evening and great place for a dinner with delicious food!","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"a year ago","text":"Very pleasant lunch in an awesome place.
The food was really good and worth the price, the atmosphere was really suggestive and especially thanks to the great view from the big windows of the landscape.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"6 mesi fa","text":"Abbiamo provato il fondue al brodo e abbiamo ADORATO l'insalata e le verdure. La carne è carne cotta nel brodo quindi non era troppo eccitante. Proverei qualcosa di diverso e meno turistico. Il condimento "francese" era fantastico! Ricordava a noi americani un ranch dressing semplificato, ma sicuramente non un ranch dressing!

La struttura è più nuova rispetto a tutto il resto che abbiamo provato in questo viaggio. Ricorda un hotel tipo "centro congressi" negli Stati Uniti. Il personale era adorabile e il mix di noci al bar è assolutamente da provare!","time":1736842377,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"2 mesi fa","text":"Il cibo è semplicemente ottimo. Ho avuto brodo di manzo con pancake, manzo su pietre calde che devi cuocere da solo, broccoli. L'atmosfera è piacevole, i panorami fantastici, i camerieri professionali.","time":1747596736,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Siamo andati due volte, la prima volta è andato tutto bene, il cibo era delizioso, il gulasch ai funghi è assolutamente da provare :)
Tuttavia, la seconda volta ci sono stati alcuni disagi - il piatto di pasta è stato servito quasi freddo, la zuppa di ramen era estremamente salata, difficilmente potevo mangiarla e non puoi davvero comparare al ramen originale in profondità di sapore. Come dessert c'era la scelta di un coppetta di gelato confezionato che, purtroppo, era vecchio e non buono così lo abbiamo restituito. Il servizio è estremamente gentile e amichevole, atmosfera piacevole. Nel complesso, alcune piccole cose potrebbero essere migliorate ma torneremo sicuramente ancora per riprovare.","time":1702802723,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Il ristorante ha un design degli interni molto accogliente e siamo stati fortunati a cenare in un tranquillo mercoledì sera.

Abbiamo ordinato Edamame, insalata Caesar, Schnitzel e zuppa di Ramen.
Tutto era molto delizioso, solo la porzione della zuppa di Ramen non era sufficiente per un piatto principale. E le patate dello Schnitzel erano un po' senza sapore.

Il nostro cameriere era molto attento e amichevole.

Una buona serata e un ottimo posto per una cena con cibo delizioso!","time":1711193544,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"it","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"un anno fa","text":"Pranzo molto piacevole in un posto fantastico.
Il cibo era davvero buono e valeva il prezzo, l'atmosfera era davvero suggestiva e soprattutto grazie alla splendida vista dalle grandi finestre sul paesaggio.","time":1702202414,"translated":true}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a 6 mois","text":"Nous avons pris la fondue au bouillon et avons ADORÉ la salade et les légumes. La viande est de la viande cuisinée dans un bouillon donc ce n'était pas très excitant. J'essaierais quelque chose d'autre et de moins touristique. La vinaigrette “French” était fantastique ! Cela nous a rappelé une sorte de sauce ranch simplifiée, mais certainement pas une sauce ranch !

L'établissement est plus récent que tout ce que nous avons essayé lors de ce voyage. Cela rappelle un type d'hôtel “centre de congrès” aux États-Unis. Le personnel était charmant et le mélange de noix au bar est un incontournable !","time":1736842377,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a 2 mois","text":"La nourriture est simplement excellente. Nous avons pris du bouillon de bœuf avec des crêpes, du bœuf sur des pierres chaudes que l'on doit cuisiner soi-même, du brocoli. L'atmosphère est agréable, la vue est superbe, les serveurs professionnels.","time":1747596736,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Nous y sommes allés 2 fois, la première fois tout s'est bien passé, la nourriture était délicieuse, le goulash aux chanterelles est à essayer :)
Cependant, la deuxième fois, il y a eu quelques déceptions - le plat de pâtes a été servi presque froid, la soupe ramen était extrêmement salée, on ne pouvait presque pas la manger et elle ne pouvait pas vraiment être comparée à un vrai ramen en termes de saveur. Pour le dessert, il y avait un choix de coupelle de glace emballée qui, malheureusement, était vieille et pas bonne donc nous l'avons retournée. Le service est extrêmement agréable et sympathique, l'atmosphère est plaisante. Dans l'ensemble, quelques détails pourraient être améliorés mais nous reviendrons certainement pour un autre essai.","time":1702802723,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Le restaurant a un design intérieur très cosy et nous avons eu la chance d'y manger un mercredi soir tranquille.

Nous avons commandé des Edamame, une salade César, un Schnitzel et une soupe Ramen.
Tout était très délicieux, juste la portion de la soupe Ramen n'était pas suffisante pour un plat principal. Et les pommes de terre avec le Schnitzel étaient un peu fades.

Notre serveur était très attentif et amical.

Une bonne soirée et un endroit idéal pour un dîner avec de la nourriture délicieuse !","time":1711193544,"translated":false},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"fr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"il y a un an","text":"Déjeuner très agréable dans un endroit impressionnant.
La nourriture était vraiment bonne et valait le prix, l'atmosphère était vraiment suggestive et particulièrement grâce à la superbe vue depuis les grandes fenêtres sur le paysage.","time":1702202414,"translated":false}]

[{"author_name":"Collette McDonald","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109429403165924285101/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTayX5cXeNGR8544uQHnh2D7SdcSlq00sXL594OAuGvLHKUByyJQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije 6 mjeseci","text":"Imali smo fondue s juhom i OBOŽAVALI salatu i povrće. Meso je meso kuhano u juhi, tako da nije bilo previše uzbudljivo. Isprobao bih nešto drugo i manje turističko. Francuski preljev bio je fantastičan! Podsjećao nas je Amerikance na pojednostavljeni ranch dressing, ali definitivno nije bio ranch dressing!

Objekt je noviji od svega što smo isprobali na ovom putovanju. Podsjeća na hotel tipa "konvencijski" centar u Sjedinjenim Američkim Državama. Osoblje je bilo divno, a mješavina orašastih plodova u baru je svakako za probati!","time":1736842377,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Sabine Vuskane","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102814169623855795164/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYydQGk0R57_0xWCZHuW_6znxFMLPonu-fQIZVzs7PL2PjASaT=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije 2 mjeseca","text":"Hrana je jednostavno odlična. Imali smo goveđu juhu s palačinkama, govedinu na vrućem kamenju koju morate sami ispeći, brokulu. Atmosfera je lijepa, pogledi su sjajni, konobari profesionalni.","time":1747596736,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Doroteja Miksa","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101421634062575998702/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfV-_6Eu0aX9mYQFQRVAUknR9Oc5lPxUyTFTVGvy_PFMcprqNj=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Došla sam tamo dvaput, prvi put je sve bilo u redu, hrana je bila ukusna, gulaš od vrganja je obavezan za probati :)
Međutim, drugi put je bilo nekoliko nedostataka - tjestenina je poslužena gotovo hladna, ramen juha bila je izuzetno slana, jedva sam ju mogla jesti i ne može se usporediti s pravim ramenom po dubini okusa. Za desert je bio izbor pakiranog sladoleda u čašici koji, nažalost, bio je star i nije bio dobar pa smo ga vratili. Usluga je iznimno draga i prijateljska, ugodna atmosfera. Sveukupno, male stvari bi se mogle poboljšati, ali sigurno ćemo ponovno doći na još jedno isprobavanje.","time":1702802723,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Anouk Janine Braune","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111569439928920748527/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWw-xqTl8DZiDEzhqHn6d8NwrbgwPd4RYWImTJJfYWYOH0QrwMl=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4","rating":4,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Restoran ima vrlo udoban interijer i imali smo sreće jesti tamo jedne tihe srijede navečer.

Naručili smo Edamame, Caesar salatu, Schnitzel i Ramen juhu.
Sve je bilo vrlo ukusno, samo što porcija Ramen juhe nije bila dovoljna za glavno jelo. A krumpir uz Schnitzel bio je malo bezukusan.

Naš konobar bio je vrlo pažljiv i ljubazan.

Dobra večer i sjajno mjesto za večeru s ukusnom hranom!","time":1711193544,"translated":true},{"author_name":"Mattia Sighel","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111194389316493434716/reviews","language":"hr","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUj540lGebo7vCM4h0BlZ7CA2M6vLAexzqelaVNI_tU_6Vq-qA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo","rating":5,"relative_time_description":"prije godinu dana","text":"Vrlo ugodan ručak na prekrasnom mjestu.
Hrana je bila doista dobra i vrijedna cijene, atmosfera je bila vrlo sugestivna, posebno zahvaljujući prekrasnom pogledu s velikih prozora na krajolik.","time":1702202414,"translated":true}]

[{"author_name":"javier montesquieu","author_url":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107077685752724958204/reviews","language":"en","original_language":"en","profile_photo_url":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2sFWZRCf-2RB-aeJpNmLpStbwAMSqr5EAm6JOzdfraOjcrg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5","rating":1,"relative_time_description":"5 months ago","text":"I asked for a room with a mountain view, and they gave me a dark one facing another building, about 3m away. The very young and not very nice lady at the reception told me when I did the reservation that my room would face the parking lot but also the mountains; not true. She also said there weren't more rooms available. When I told the owner the next morning I would leave, she told me that she would get me another room...oh, now that I leave there are rooms available??
Also, dining room was poorly lit, sad, and the service was appaling: not a single hello, smile...salad bar was pension level, although bfast was pretty good.
